   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl334a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>
                        <choice>
                           <orig>Nashvill</orig>
                           <reg>Nashville</reg>
                        </choice> tennessee</name>
                     <name>mr <choice>
                           <abbr>A</abbr>
                           <expan>Adam</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                           <orig>ferguson</orig>
                           <reg>Fergusson</reg>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </opener>
            <p>this is the <date>4 of June 1850</date> we <choice>
                  <orig>ar</orig>
                  <reg>are</reg>
               </choice> all well at this time my life is at stake and I <choice>
                  <orig>wat</orig>
                  <reg>want</reg>
               </choice> you to to send or fetch me two of the Best <choice>
                  <orig>pistoles</orig>
                  <reg>pistols</reg>
               </choice> that you can <choice>
                  <orig>git</orig>
                  <reg>get</reg>
               </choice> in nashvill <name>Ross</name> came in <del type="overstrike">f</del> the fall and <choice>
                  <orig>thretend</orig>
                  <reg>threatened</reg>
               </choice> to <choice>
                  <orig>shut</orig>
                  <reg>shoot</reg>
               </choice>
               <del type="overstrike">be</del> me <choice>
                  <orig>twist</orig>
                  <reg>twice</reg>
               </choice> or three times and drew a large <choice>
                  <orig>hickry</orig>
                  <reg>hickory</reg>
               </choice> stick on me and Swore that he would kill me we are <choice>
                  <orig>dun planten</orig>
                  <reg>done planting</reg>
               </choice> corn I believe that I   <choice>
                  <orig>shant</orig>
                  <reg>shouldn't</reg>
               </choice>
               <choice>
                  <orig>wright</orig>
                  <reg>write</reg>
               </choice> any more at this time only that he drew his pistol or started to But he did not quite <unclear>cumet</unclear> do not <choice>
                  <orig>for git</orig>
                  <reg>forget</reg>
               </choice> to Bring them if you <choice>
                  <orig>pleas</orig>
                  <reg>please</reg>
               </choice> Sir</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>yours and <unclear>soforth</unclear>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name>Samuel D Hughes</name>
               </signed>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl334b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>Mr Adam Fergusson</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Nashville</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Ten</abbr>
                        <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
